FROM python:3.11-slim AS builder

WORKDIR /app

RUN apt-get update && \
    apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends curl && \
    rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

COPY requirements.txt download_model.py ./

RUN pip install --no-cache-dir --target=/app/dependencies -r requirements.txt && \
    python download_model.py

FROM python:3.11-slim AS production

LABEL maintainer="ml-team@example.com"
LABEL org.opencontainers.image.source="https://github.com/org/ml-inference"
LABEL org.opencontainers.image.description="Python ML inference service with FastAPI"

RUN apt-get update && \
    apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends curl && \
    rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/* && \
    addgroup --system appgroup && \
    adduser --system --ingroup appgroup appuser

WORKDIR /app

COPY --from=builder /app/dependencies /usr/local/lib/python3.11/site-packages
COPY --from=builder /app/model.pt ./
COPY . .

USER appuser

EXPOSE 8000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=10s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:8000/health || exit 1

CMD ["python", "-m", "uvicorn", "main:app", "--host", "0.0.0.0", "--port", "8000"]
